data.description: Check Out the New Carpet! This fresh and attractive home sits  in a quiet, well maintained neighborhood and has a bonus auxiliary studio building! Added value! This home has so much of what you want in a home. With a well maintained exterior  &  large private yard with pond plus room to spare for play or gardening, you know immediately this place means HOME. The 4 bedrooms/ 3 baths are just the beginning of all the great spaces, plus both a traditional fireplace (upstairs) and a pellet stove (downstairs).,This means added benefits of being very energy efficient. Large open living and dining areas not only have windows for bringing in the sunshine reflected on the beautiful rich floor, but there is a lovely traditional fireplace for a focal point making a great gathering space. The room is large enough to host a crowd and yet it feel intimate and welcoming. The kitchen has a pass through to create just that separation of spaces but allows for easy flow between rooms, wile still open to dining.  There are plenty of cupboards in this well organized kitchen with lots of counter space. ft full basement with 3 bedrooms plus additional storage rooms means you have space galore!  The two car garage is spacious enough to house a workbench and storage shelving all around.  Large lot has a large landscape pond and plenty of space for gardening and play.  The extra bonus here is a  finished 240 sq ft bonus building. This studio space has lovely wood detail, plenty of windows  vaulted ceiling, plenty of lighting, and heat for all season use.  It has been used as both a recording studio, study area, and workout gym.  No matter what you are looking for in a home, this property has it.
